            <h2 class="h2 text-line grow-0">Our History</h2>
        </div>
    <div class="prose">
	<p>Midas Touch School of Excellence was founded with a vision to redefine quality education and nurture future-ready citizens. Since our inception, we have proudly marched forward, making significant strides in the field of education. With several years of dedicated service, we have become a trusted institution known for academic excellence, student empowerment, and holistic development.</p>
	<p>Our journey began with a simple yet powerful belief — that education is not merely the learning of facts, but the training of the mind to think. Guided by this philosophy and in academic partnership with Next Education India Pvt. Ltd., we have created a learning environment that is dynamic, inclusive, and forward-thinking.</p>
	<p>Over the years, we have continuously evolved, embracing innovation in teaching methodologies, technology integration, and student-centered learning practices. We have celebrated numerous milestones — from academic achievements to cultural successes — all of which are a testament to the dedication of our educators, the trust of our parents, and the hard work of our students.</p>
	<p>Today, Midas Touch School of Excellence stands as a beacon of learning, committed to shaping responsible, curious, and confident young minds who are ready to take on the challenges of an ever-changing world.</p>
          </div>
      </div>
